{
  "3082000": {
    "name": "装备之路: 铁匠传奇",
    "steam_appid": 3082000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/3f620d209b45789ad2925b1b416a45d5.avif?t=1765233497\" width=1560 height=134 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身为铁匠军师，你将亲自站在「欧洛波罗斯时间轴」上写下行动脚本，指挥每一场战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人的行动会以「每秒」为单位显示，清楚标出接下来 20 秒内「会发生什么事」以及「什么时候发生」，让你一眼看穿整场战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >善用这 20 秒的时间去：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抢在敌人释放致命技能之前先出手打断</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >串起多个行动，触发彼此呼应的词缀反应</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅规划每把武器在时间轴上的位置，还要思考要先修哪一把，为长期战术做准备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同武器的重量与类型，会直接影响「挥击所需的时间」。<br>如果你能精确掌握出手时机，就能抢得先机，甚至在时间轴上引爆意料之外的连锁反应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胜利或死亡，全都压在这短短的 20 秒里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的战术，会带领冒险者走向胜利，还是把他们推向终点？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/611f6e913fc602ffcde8f08d6ca252b7.poster.avif?t=1765233497\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/611f6e913fc602ffcde8f08d6ca252b7.webm?t=1765233497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/611f6e913fc602ffcde8f08d6ca252b7.mp4?t=1765233497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/66c014f22944b529d4a06bd76ab040b0.avif?t=1765233497\" width=1560 height=134 /></span>传说级的锻造师不只是「做出」武器；真正的高手，是从选对模具和素材开始，一锤一击敲出武器的个性与灵魂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中，从强大的敌人身上收集各种独特素材。<br>每一种素材都有自己的特性与倾向，让武器组合拥有近乎无限的变化可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择合适的武器「模具」，再把素材镶进对应插槽，让词缀与武器特性彼此产生联动。<br>尝试不同的「模具 × 素材」组合，锻造出真正定义你这一套流派核心的武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器的品质，不只是冰冷的数值，而是由你的「搭配」与「设计」所决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次挥下铁锤，都是对流派方向的一次抉择；每一把完工的武器，都是你理念与冒险旅程的具现化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/cdf845e15ba8407a87c194170008c2f8.poster.avif?t=1765233497\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/cdf845e15ba8407a87c194170008c2f8.webm?t=1765233497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/cdf845e15ba8407a87c194170008c2f8.mp4?t=1765233497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/afee3b603f0b5d015662b827e18c5713.avif?t=1765233497\" width=1560 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身为锻造师，你也能通过超过 400 颗天赋节点和多条成长分支，一点一滴打造属于自己的「锻造风格」，不只是变强，更是在亲手锻造全新的作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些天赋不会因为一轮冒险结束就被重置。<br>相反地，每一次冒险、每一次死亡，都会成为你成长的养分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些天赋会让你在满血时成为输出爆炸的玻璃大炮，在残血时则摇身一变成为稳如高墙的坦克；<br>也有天赋专精于特定武器类型，让武器模具能够随着你的成长一同变强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甚至还存在高风险高收益的极限流派——每次攻击都会削减自己的生命，但换来的，是随着战斗时间不断疯狂攀升的伤害。<br>你可以让每一次死亡都变成燃料，在反复尝试中，一步步靠近最适合自己的流派。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，强度不只是数值和随机的产物，<br>更是由你的「点数分配」与「设计选择」亲手塑造出来的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一点天赋点，都是你对这套 Build 的亲笔注解；每一条你解锁的天赋路线，都是你的思考方式与冒险旅程，被清晰地刻在盘面上的轨迹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/17bbdfd05961476dde42c1afe31de58e.poster.avif?t=1765233497\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/17bbdfd05961476dde42c1afe31de58e.webm?t=1765233497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/17bbdfd05961476dde42c1afe31de58e.mp4?t=1765233497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/f15a94472484a6728d7985263ed0638e.avif?t=1765233497\" width=1560 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >肚子饿是没办法锻造、也没办法冒险的。<br>每次出发前，记得先去餐馆好好吃一顿再上路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不只是主厨会端出特制菜单，旁边还有一只超级挑剔的猫咪美食评论家。<br>它对料理的评价，将会左右你这次冒险能带走哪些强力 Buff。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食材会在多次冒险之间累积：打倒怪物、完成事件，都会带回新的食材。<br>根据每种食材的特性去调整配比，命中合适的区间，就有机会做出评价极高的料理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吃饭并不是一个只有「最佳解」的数值游戏，对饥肠辘辘的冒险者来说，根本不存在所谓唯一正确的一餐。<br>有时候稍微冒点险、尝试平时不会放在一起的食材组合，反而能换来强大到夸张的增益——当然，也有可能带来可怕的副作用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一餐，都是为下一场战斗做准备：<br>你会选择吃得安全、稳稳前进，还是品尝近乎禁忌的力量，并承担随之而来的一切代价？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/6ededee206712d3a2187185ac6c59dd8.poster.avif?t=1765233497\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/6ededee206712d3a2187185ac6c59dd8.webm?t=1765233497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/6ededee206712d3a2187185ac6c59dd8.mp4?t=1765233497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/7e1d51d25189ceb42212118c84cf3536.avif?t=1765233497\" width=1560 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一片未知的大地，一次踩下一格六边形地块，慢慢把整张世界地图拼出来。<br>若是踏出了自己的实力范围，你将面临「灾厄」、更强的敌人，以及节奏全面加速的高压战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规划路线时必须步步为营，看似普通的路径中，藏着相对安全的道路、惊险的捷径，以及只有眼尖玩家才能发现的隐藏宝物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一张地图中都散布着超过 80 种随机事件，等着考验你的临场反应与小聪明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以靠三寸不烂之舌谈来装备，也有可能一个选项点错，就把自己送进一场残酷硬仗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择哪条路、承担什么后果——全都由你自己决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/2adba3999bcfec49930197a239042d82.poster.avif?t=1765233497\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/2adba3999bcfec49930197a239042d82.webm?t=1765233497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082000/extras/2adba3999bcfec49930197a239042d82.mp4?t=1765233497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
